Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有自己那么有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三年级是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班级是二年级开始跟班的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道学生们更多的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  看以前的业务日志不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙一年级的时候的日志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好神气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宇佐在那个时候就那么高了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,镜还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲已死  父亲分居
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在与亲戚住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下面是作业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,写篇关于爸爸妈妈的作文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洗好手过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  林志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作业做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可写了三页又五行多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重凛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈每天早上都会给我系头发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在生日的时候给我买的发饰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢妈妈给我梳头发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在什么都不知道的情况下做了过分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,推我吧  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与亲戚住在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎么样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这些都是因没有双亲而渴望亲情的行为的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想进行反转的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不痛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉今天的老师真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师一直都很温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是很不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱我到教室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛  去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,午休马上就要结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了是美美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  然后呢  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}啊  抱着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对待学生该平等  这是作为教师理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天泳池开放啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  从刚才开始一直在傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于游泳课的注意事项
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定要把这个交给家人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,传到后面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好交给亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是侵犯隐私
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,镜知道  才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈每天早上都会给我系头发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢妈妈给我梳头发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想被人知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,花样游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狗刨式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:10:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  在同情我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我温柔是因为我很可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还那么高兴的我就像笨蛋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么爱撒娇的九重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后都没有对过眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  道歉本身就会更加伤害九重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小黑的体操服真肥大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一年级的时候买了大号的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是因为马上就会长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有在成长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人偶体型更加适合礼服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:13:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想变得像美美这样大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叮咚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我也按一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  九重也排好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师再见  大家再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宇佐  镜  可以打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们一定要遵从老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是童贞你以为你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小黑  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才想好好道歉  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会帮你劝告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了九重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很傲慢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  就这么过分对待九重下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青木老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛受到伤害不是因为被人说自己没有双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…小凛…爱上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这种事情自己去想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,镜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,童贞  包茎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我老早之前就在小凛身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别一人先走  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先走的是小黑你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重受伤不是因为没有双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打…打扰了  忽然来访
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是双桥小学三年一班的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名为青木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得我已经拒绝家庭访问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…是偶然路过而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想来打一下招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛正外出中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有很好闻的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好收拾过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…今天双亲不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛的事情的话  我洗耳恭听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说凛失去母亲  寄宿在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很失礼  不过作为班主任想掌握情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以告诉我详情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家原本是凛与她妈妈两人居住的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是凛妈妈的表弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在四年前因事故而失去了双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当时还健在的凛的妈妈收养了还是未成年的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是九重被收养
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在住在这家里的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就我与凛两人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重与年轻男人两人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像你非常疼爱凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是这样的孩子  代替双亲担心她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师也得小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,林志  蛋卖光了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛  这样很失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有说奇怪的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有做说出来会困扰的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有做过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  好好面向老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  九重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重的家比想象中还要温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有双亲也不冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是很好的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这心情是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,林志  觉得老师如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  如凛所说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像非常喜欢凛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话不会特意到家里来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真像笨蛋  为什么要来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师担心学生  有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,担心我  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为九重是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛我的话  不会饶恕你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…对我来说初次的接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…早熟小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起观看烟火大会最佳地点  果然还是神社后面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过烟火本身被竹林围着  基本上看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竹林  竹林  刺人的凛
